                           hes they purposed wyth the sword and fyre to ouercome at the cytie, felowes of thy madnesse and mischiefe, assembled together the laste nighte in the house of M. Lecea. Darest thou deny thys? why spekest not? If thou woldeste denye it, I can proue it. For I se here in the Senate some of thē: that were there together with the. O good lorde where be we? what a common weale haue we? In what citie lyue we? There are here, euen here amonge

