                  Here begynneth the famous Cronicle of warre, whyche the Romaynes hadde agaynst Iugurth vsurper of the kyngedome of Numidie: whiche Cronicle is compiled in Laten by the renowmed Romayne Saluste: and translated into englyshe by syr alexander Barklaye prieste. And nowe perused and corrected by Thomas Paynell.
